{"tid":2053203,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知道點解10號風球＋黑雨難以同時發出","createTime":"2020-06-06T05:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T20:34:27.000Z","uid":108894,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3417dff341820919e85173d554daeb39b3a69898","tid":2053203,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:32:55.000Z","msg":"以我所知<br />\n1. 天文台嘅雨量計係直立，當發出10號時風勢太大，雨水打橫飛落唔到雨量計<br />\n2. 北半球熱帶氣旋系統最大雨係南面，但危險半圓係北面，最近幾次10號全部都係西登而北面掃過香港。相反南面雖然雨大但屬於可航半圓，多數得8號至9號風力，而且南面掃過香港時熱帶氣旋已經上岸而減弱，香港風勢不大<br />\n<br />\n但呢兩個警告同時出現唔係零機會<br />\n1. 強度達強颱風或以上<br />\n2. 西貢登陸橫越新界<br />\n3. 颱風移速偏慢<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPs 暴雨警告出現以黎最多係10號加紅雨 (約克同山竹)"},{"pid":"5d88c6e8e6f0c95d5d12fee128adb2c6c868ecd1","tid":2053203,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:35:57.000Z","msg":"因為大交合係商務及經濟發展局管<br />\n掛咗10號之後，掛咩雨都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>"},{"pid":"a429132480d9be644e3bd8e31c1210581e25616a","tid":2053203,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:37:04.000Z","msg":"因為今日係星期六"},{"pid":"cae5ce4ee01bb6229d4b0231ae7b8fb7776e5d48","tid":2053203,"uid":109971,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:48:43.000Z","msg":"因為今日係星期六"},{"pid":"f0d530a9a945147ff762444f1febb5e8cb13255d","tid":2053203,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:05:00.000Z","msg":"係認真討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb0c2d91e64e5afbf1647a2e308fe886990abd4","tid":2053203,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5d88c6e8e6f0c95d5d12fee128adb2c6c868ecd1","tid":2053203,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:35:57.000Z","msg":"因為大交合係商務及經濟發展局管<br />\n掛咗10號之後，掛咩雨都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:05:23.000Z","msg":"又真係wor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b29df15837be64749d25aa92e9b307f7b12a02","tid":2053203,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:09:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">啊</span></strong>&hellip;寄相思風雨中"},{"pid":"cac59a8d51689ff89549d3b60d7443d799f873ce","tid":2053203,"uid":155902,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T15:35:40.000Z","msg":"以我所知, 成熟颱風中心一般應該唔多垂直對流發展暴雨區, 所以近風眼壁位應該就算有雨都好難去到黑色暴雨個Level"},{"pid":"ef28c5a66c5a24ca92aae82f91366a0725f52c51","tid":2053203,"uid":245282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T15:45:50.000Z","msg":"風眼無雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個風九號十號多數一滴雨都無 但大陸個邊應該就好大雨"},{"pid":"0bcce084fd436ae1f78275516716ba9110bdb8e4","tid":2053203,"uid":166032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T17:01:39.000Z","msg":"雖然理論上係獨立系統，可以同時發出<br />\n但實用上，除左樓主講嘅狀況，兩樣野都係講有危險唔好出街，只再其中一個生效已經達到目標？"},{"pid":"83d0c52bfb3225ea68b48fa7f5df2e33c47dd52f","tid":2053203,"uid":13914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T20:34:27.000Z","msg":"黑色暴雨警告加紅色火災危險警告難度應該比你高好多"}]}